## `Proxy`
> `Proxy`用于修改修改默认操作，对目标对象进行代理

```javascript
let obj = new Proxy({}, {

  get(target, props, receiver) {
    return Reflex.get(target, props, receiver)
  },
  set(target, props, value, receiver) {
    return Reflect.set(target, props, value, receiver);
  }
})

